data.description: MOVE IN READY! This gorgeous, low maintenance townhome in The VUE at Celebration Pointe is ready for you to make your new home or the ultimate GATOR game day retreat. This residence features a spacious, open layout with living space all located on the first floor plus a garden patio off the dining room and a rear garage. The large great room opens to the kitchen / dining room with European inspired cabinetry, quartz counter tops and custom tile backsplash. Upstairs you’ll find all three bedrooms + convenient laundry closet. Luxury vinyl plank flooring is throughout this home with tile in each bathroom. The owner’s suite features a large, walk-in closet and custom tile bath with large shower, and frameless glass enclosure. This residence is close to shopping, dining and entertainment at Celebration Pointe’s Promenade with Regal Cinemas, Prime & Pearl, Spurrier’s and the new Alachua County Sports Events Center. Enjoy a low maintenance lifestyle while living in the heart of Gainesville’s prime entertainment and retail location! Close to University of Florida, UF Health Shands Hospital, VA and easy access to I-75. A dedicated bus line also runs through Celebration Pointe with service to campus and hospitals. Community amenities include an open air cabana with summer kitchen, large resort style pool, jacuzzi and 24 hour security patrol. Community backs to 700 acre Kanapaha Preserve with trails to enjoy. You wont want to miss this opportunity!
